Wiltin Windwalker is a renegade ranger, who descided to become a poacher. Now the ranger guild in Kithicor Forest has put a price on his head, and implores all rangers to kill him onsite. Wiltin (AKA Wiltin the theif) is a rare spawn in the OOT. His place holder is the buccaneer at the small pirate camp. When killed Wiltin will usually drop the Quiver of Kelethin.
